videos.description: Kevaughn Allen buries a 3-pointer in transition off the assist from Kasey Hill.
videos.headline: Allen knocks down the pull-up 3-pointer

videos.description: Kasey Hill steals a pass and then sprints full court for a huge dunk.
videos.headline: Kasey Hill destroys the rim

videos.description: South Carolina's Duane Notice knocks down a 3-pointer after he is left open in transition.
videos.headline: Notice puts Gators on notice as he drains a 3-pointer

videos.description: KeVaughn Allen throws down a monster dunk after getting a steal on the other end.
videos.headline: Allen obliterates the rim with thunderous jam

videos.description: South Carolina Head Coach Frank Martin praises team for battling back after falling behind by 12 earlier in the first half.
videos.headline: Frank Martin praises team for battling in the first half

videos.description: Devin Robinson converts the and-1 after a beautiful pass from Keith Stone.
videos.headline: Robinson gets and-1 to go

videos.description: Sindarius Thornwell anticipates the inbound pass, steals it and throws it down on the other end.
videos.headline: Thornwell steals the inbound pass and throws it down on the other end

videos.description: Florida coach Mike White praises his team for their toughness and togetherness after a dominant second half.
videos.headline: White: Toughness wills Gators to win

videos.description: KeVaughn Allen's 26 points leads Florida past South Carolina 81-66.
videos.headline: KeVaughn Allen's 26 points leads Florida past South Carolina 81-66

videos.description: Devin Robinson adds 14 points to KeVaughn Allen's 26 points to lead No. 13 Florida to a 81-66 victory over South Carolina.
videos.headline: KeVaughn Allen's 26 points leads Gators to ninth straight win
